Requirement
-----------
- Linux (being developed under CentOS 6.x)
- g++
- GNU readline
- boost-regex, boost-devel
- json-cpp (https://jsoncpp.sourceforge.net/)
- Ruby
- Ruby on Rails (TBD)

Build
-----
- Download and build json-cpp (latest 0.6.0-rc2).
-- Copy include/json and lib/linux*/libjson-gcc-4.4.7_libmt.a under 'genclidb'
   source tree.
- Download quagga(or zebra) routing suite and extract source tree somewhere.
- Go to quagga protocol directory and run "cli.json/quagga.cli2json.rb" script
  to generate from *.c file to *.cli.json.
- Copy *.cli.json file to cli.json/ directory.
- do 'make'.

